Class DJIDeformInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • dji.sdk.api.MainController.DJIDeformInfo

  • public class DJIDeformInfo
extends java.lang.Object

    Dji Deform Info Class

    This structure is designed for deforming. Please remember the Inspire Series is the only drone could deform. This data structure will record all the status of the deform status and whether the deform protection is opened or not.
    Version:
    V2.4.0
    Author:
    DJI Software
